{"word":"Uzziah","slug":"uzziah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Uzziah</b> <a href=\"#/H5814\">H5814</a><br/><a href=\"#/H5818\">H5818</a> <br/> 1. Called Azariah:<br/> - King of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=21'>2Ki 14:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=2'>2Ki 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=1'>2Ch 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=3'>2Ch 26:3</a> <br/> - Rebuilds Elath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=22'>2Ki 14:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=2'>2Ch 26:2</a> <br/> - Reigns righteously<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=3'>2Ki 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=5'>2Ch 26:5</a> <br/> - Defeats the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=7'>2Ch 26:7</a> <br/> - Takes tribute from the Ammonites; strengthens the kingdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=8'>2Ch 26:8</a> <br/> - Strengthens the fortifications of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=9'>2Ch 26:9</a> <br/> - Promotes cattle raising and agriculture<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=10'>2Ch 26:10</a> <br/> - Military establishment of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=15'>2Ch 26:15</a> <br/> - Is presumptuous in burning incense; stricken with leprosy; quarantined<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=21'>2Ch 26:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=5'>2Ki 15:5</a> <br/> - Jotham regent during quarantine of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=5'>2Ki 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=21'>2Ch 26:21</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=7'>2Ki 15:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=23'>2Ch 26:23</a> <br/> - History of, written by Isaiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=22'>2Ch 26:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=1'>Isa 1:1</a> <br/> - Earthquake in the reign of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=1'>Amo 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=5'>Zec 14:5</a> <br/> 2. Son of Uriel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=24'>1Ch 6:24</a><br/> 3. Father of Jehonathan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=25'>1Ch 27:25</a><br/> 4. A priest, puts away his Gentile wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=21'>Ezr 10:21</a><br/> 5. Father of Athaiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=4'>Neh 11:4</a>"}]}